comment._content:
I think that Harrington Lane no longer exists.  I think it was under what is now the Four Seasons Hotel in the area bounded by Harrington Street, George Street and the Cahill Expressway - although it probably used to cross the line of what is now the Cahill -  I'm trying to find an old online map to confirm this.

It is probably less than 50 metres from where the city office of State Records NSW currently sits.
